{"word":"ὑπερέχω","slug":"ὑπερέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὑπερέχω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὑπέρ\">ὑπέρ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχω\">ἔχω</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> ‘be at a point that is superior’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of rank or status <b>have control, govern <a href='B:520 13:1'>Ro 13:1</a>; <a href='B:670 2:13'>1 Pt 2:13</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of qualitative advantage: <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <b>be superior to, surpass <a href='B:570 4:7'>Phil 4:7</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b>be more important than <a href='B:570 2:3'>2:3</a>.</b> As noun <el>τὸ ὑπερέχον</el> the surpassingness = the surpassing value <b><a href='B:570 3:8'>3:8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπερεντυγχάνω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὑπερηφανία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}